reviews.text:
等我又講講平時返工lunch日常🙆🏻‍♀️
除左光輝圍，同同事最常去嘅就係KCC間夏麵館，12點9前埋單仲有85折，我地最鐘意食嘅就係老上海炒麵，次次都要叫2碟先夠喉🤣🤣
-
☆ 老上海炒麵  HK$66
▪炒麵即係粗身上海麵
▪上碟熱辣辣 香噴噴好夠鑊氣
▪每條麵都炒到入味 顏色均勻
▪麵條夾落略嫌有少少碎同較油
▪味道啱啱好 醬汁甜甜地唔會好咸
▪份量算大碟 配料肉絲荀白菜都好多
▪次次去食都必點哩個 推介俾大家😚👍👍
-
📍夏麵館
葵涌葵昌路72-76號活@KCC 8樓803號舖

在葵涌上班的話，多數都在這裡吃午餐，日常都比較多人，因為選擇不多。食物質素不太穩定，價錢又不是特別便宜，中規中矩。
我點了擔擔麵，份量不錯，湯底正常辣，不過湯府有點兒浠身，花生味道不太足夠。午市麵餐都會配一款小食，點了小籠包，有2隻，不錯。
朋友點了口水雞配陽春麵，口水雞份量正常，不過也有點兒辣，會吃辣的才好點。
另外一位朋友點了炒年糕，年糕都是厚切，很彈牙，很軟熟，味道不錯，值得一試。
炸薰魚要另加30元，覺得有點兒太貴，不過也不錯，很香脆的。
午市套餐都有附送飲品，當然，點汽水要再額外付費。點了暖豆漿，有點兒太甜。
價錢適中，食品有水準及服務不錯。
環境較一般食店清靜。價格合理。
好吃，份量多！價錢合理

reviews.text: The ground floor has the best restaurants imo

A factory building converted into yet another food and retail complex filled mostly with typical chain stores. It comes from a very regretable government policy of "revitalising industrial buildings", which in effect allows property developers to change the land usage from industrial (buy low) to commerical (let out high) without a public tendering process.
Footbridge between KCC and MTR station. There are lot of restaurant in this building.
New shopping place.

reviews.text: High-end commercial buildings, fast food chain and restaurant on the ground. There are two towers established here. Different companies incorporated here. Open University's classrooms had also occupied in some floors here.
Worth going to the highest floor
Very good location which connect to MTR station, very convenient. A lot of shops here, you no need to go outside during hot summer or bad weather day. Place and toilets are clean.
Modern shopping center, attached to an MTR station.

This is a brand new commercial complex among old factory buildings.  It is good to have a walk and some food there.  Note that there is a covered and air-conditioned walkway connecting directly to the platform level (Exit E?) of MTR Kwai Hing Station.
